{"tid":405195,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"省港旗兵劫香檳大廈錶行　重案埋伏一網成擒","createTime":"2017-09-18T15:54:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T16:26:41.000Z","uid":20933,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fcbf44a5ac1c3e20acd5945e7da0c75e78f6fbcc","tid":405195,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T15:54:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170918/large/1505747290_823c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170918%2Flarge%2F1505747290_823c.jpg&h=b2556e1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n尖沙嘴金巴利道香檳大廈，晚上9時許發生行劫案。多名賊匪乘坐一輛私家車到場，打劫地下一間錶行，但警方西九龍重案組探員接獲線報，預先到場埋伏，並趁賊人下手之際，即上前截查拘捕。其間匪徒激烈反抗與警員糾纏，最後至少4名匪徒被擒。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指，涉案賊匪包括來自支那的省港旗兵，警員事後翻查閉路電視調查，並搜查涉事負責接應的該輛私家車。<br />\n<br />\n涉事錶行的老闆娘事後講述經過，表示事發前見多名戴鴨舌帽的可疑男子在錶行外張望，欲對廚窗內多隻名錶打主意，詎料他們準備下手之際，大批埋伏的警員即一湧而上把匪徒制服拘捕，老闆娘見事發亦即時拉閘。"},{"pid":"c59a817d413c0db7550edcdda07faea799adf6aa","tid":405195,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T15:54:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170918&amp;guid=57227265&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170918%26guid%3D57227265%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=UzWHiFDZ68nYT9RT6v2vL75jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=cbf8a457\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170918%26guid%3D57227265%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=cb2fe106\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170918&amp;guid=57227265&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"17a762a70483da52284cb63fc885ea034f9b461b","tid":405195,"uid":49392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T15:56:20.000Z","msg":"咁唔包容支那人"},{"pid":"c3e50b7